Rating: 4
I've made this salad several times, and always to ecstatic reviews. There are so many interesting flavors in it that people tend to eat quite a lot. While it nominally serves 10, I've seen 6 people polish it off. I wouldn't substitute for the arugula, which adds a lot of depth of flavor, or for the goat cheese, which is the high bright flavor note in this composition.

