Rating: 4
For my husband's birthday, we served this wonderful salad along with the rest of the March '99 Birthday part menu. This is the best salad that I have made in a long time. It is very true to its preparation steps. It was so good that some of my guests wanted a third helping. Everyone was especially thrilled with the migas (croutons). The goat cheese was also a great idea. If you can't find it, you could substitute a creamy feta.